Package: jwt-hack
Version: 2.6.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: make, openssl, rust, perl, pkg-config
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://jwt-hack.hahwul.com/
Description: JWT security testing and exploitation tool
 jwt-hack is a command-line tool for testing JSON Web Tokens,
 including signing, forging, and exploiting vulnerabilities like
 algorithm confusion, kid injection, and more.
